  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This trial aims to evaluate the efficacy of three experimental dentifrices to remove denture
      biofilm. Complete denture wearers will be instructed to brush their dentures with a specific
      toothbrush and four compositions: (1) A proprietary denture-specific paste (active
      comparator); (2) 0.2% chloramine T; (3) 1.0% chloramine T; (4) 0.01% fluorosurfactant. Each
      treatment will be used for periods of 7 days, and participants will be randomized to use them
      according to one of four sequences.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
